      "retweeted_tweet_id": null,
      "text": "Veterans Day is a time to honor the extraordinary men and women who have served in the armed forces. \n\nAt CBP, we are privileged to have a workforce in which roughly one-third are military veterans – patriots who have continued their service by safeguarding America’s borders. We also honor the families and loved ones of our veteran colleagues whose sacrifices and steadfast support make their service possible.\n \nYour unwavering spirit of service inspires us each and every day. Your grit and commitment to leading by example ensures that CBP’s mission remains steadfast and resolute.\n\nThank you all for your service, your sacrifice, and your unbridled commitment. You embody the spirit that defines our nation and our agency. You inspire us all.",
      "text_resolved": "Veterans Day is a time to honor the extraordinary men and women who have served in the armed forces. \n\nAt CBP, we are privileged to have a workforce in which roughly one-third are military veterans – patriots who have continued their service by safeguarding America’s borders. We also honor the families and loved ones of our veteran colleagues whose sacrifices and steadfast support make their service possible.\n \nYour unwavering spirit of service inspires us each and every day. Your grit and commitment to leading by example ensures that CBP’s mission remains steadfast and resolute.\n\nThank you all for your service, your sacrifice, and your unbridled commitment. You embody the spirit that defines our nation and our agency. You inspire us all.",
